       <script defer="" src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/openlayers/2.13.1/OpenLayers.js">
       </script>
       <script defer="" src="/Scripts/Project/map.js">
       </script>
       <script>
        $(function () {
 
             // 廣告輪播
             $('#banner .flexslider').flexslider({
                 pauseOnAction: false
             });
 
             $(window).keyup(function (e) {
                 var code = (e.keyCode ? e.keyCode : e.which);
                 if (code == 9 && $('#banner .flexslider .slides li a:focus').length) {
 
                     var data = $('#banner .flexslider').data('flexslider');
                     var dataIndex = $('#banner .flexslider .slides li a:focus').data('index');
                     var slider = data.slides[dataIndex];
 
                     data.flexAnimate(dataIndex, true);
 
                     $(slider).css("border", "1px solid #333");
                     $(slider).css("border-style", "dotted");
                 }
             });
 
             $('#banner .flexslider .slides li a').blur(function (e) {
                 var data = $('#banner .flexslider').data('flexslider');
 
                 for (var i = 0; i < data.slides.length; i++) {
                     var slider = data.slides[i];
 
                     $(slider).css("border", "none");
                     $(slider).css("border-style", "none");
                 }
 
                 data.play();
             });
 
             // 載入地圖
             initMap();
 
             var epsg4326 = new OpenLayers.Projection("EPSG:4326");
             var projectTo = map.getProjectionObject();
             var vectorLayer = new OpenLayers.Layer.Vector("套疊圖層", {
                 displayInLayerSwitcher: false,
                 isBaseLayer: false,
             });
 
             map.setCenter(new OpenLayers.LonLat(lon, lat).transform(
                 new OpenLayers.Projection("EPSG:4326"),
                 map.getProjectionObject()
             ), 6);
 
             loadConstructionRoad();
 
             var controls = {
                 selector: new OpenLayers.Control.SelectFeature(vectorLayer, { onSelect: createPopup, onUnselect: destroyPopup })
             };
 
             function createPopup(feature) {
                 feature.popup = new OpenLayers.Popup.FramedCloud("pop",
                     feature.geometry.getBounds().getCenterLonLat(),
                     null,
                     '<div class="markerContent">' + feature.attributes.description + '</div>',
                     null,
                     true,
                     function () { controls['selector'].unselectAll(); }
                 );
 
                 map.addPopup(feature.popup);
             }
 
             function destroyPopup(feature) {
                 feature.popup.destroy();
                 feature.popup = null;
             }
 
             map.addControl(controls['selector']);
             controls['selector'].activate();
 
             // 施工路段查詢
             $("#btnConstructionRoad").click(function () {
                 loadConstructionRoad();
             });
 
             // 載入施工路段資料
             function loadConstructionRoad() {
 
                 vectorLayer.removeFeatures(vectorLayer.features);
 
                 var ddlConstructionRoadCity = $("#main_main_ddlConstructionRoadCity");
                 var url = "/api/GetExpresswayInterchangeSet?city=" + ddlConstructionRoadCity.val();
 
                 $.ajax({
                     url: encodeURI(url),
                     type: "GET",
                     dataType: "json",
                     success: function (jData) {
 
                         var i = 0;
 
                         $.each(jData, function () {
                             var lon = jData[i].Longitude;
                             var lat = jData[i].Latitude;
                             var des = "";
 
                             des += "<div style='font-family: 微軟正黑體; font-size: 10px'>";
                             des += "<div><label>縣　　市：</label>" + jData[i].City + "</div>";
                             des += "<div><label>施工單位：</label>" + jData[i].ConstructionOrg + "</div>";
                             des += "<div><label>施工地點：</label>" + jData[i].ConstructionLocation + "</div>";
                             des += "<div><label>施工內容：</label>" + jData[i].ConstructionContent + "<span style='margin-left: 5px'><a href='/sites/ch/modules/constructionroad/constructionroad_details?node=a9cf3c6e-c6b5-4115-82bb-aa8beed2e82d&id=" + jData[i].Id + "' title='瀏覽詳細資料'><i class=\"fa fa-search\"></i></a></span></div>";
                             des += "<div><label>動工時間：</label>" + jData[i].StartDate + "</div>";
                             des += "<div><label>完工時間：</label>" + jData[i].CompletionDate + "</div>";
                             des += "<div class='text-right'></div>";
 
                             des += "</div>";
 
                             var feature = new OpenLayers.Feature.Vector(
                                     new OpenLayers.Geometry.Point(lon, lat).transform(epsg4326, projectTo),
                                     { description: des },
                                     { externalGraphic: '/Content/ch/images/map_warning.png', graphicHeight: 20, graphicWidth: 20, graphicXOffset: -12, graphicYOffset: -25 }
                                 );
 
                             vectorLayer.addFeatures(feature);
 
                             i++;
                         });
                     },
                     error: function (msg) {
                         console.log(msg);
                     }
                 });
 
                         map.addLayer(vectorLayer);
                     }
         });
       </script>
      </div>
     </div>

    <script>
     $(function () {
 
             $(".flexnav").flexNav();
 
             $('#navbar-menu .dropdown-menu .flexslider').flexslider({
                 animation: "slide",
                 animationLoop: false,
                 slideshow: false,
                 itemWidth: 350,
                 itemMargin: 15,
                 minItems: 5,
                 maxItems: 5
             });
 
             $('#navbar-menu .dropdown.mega-dropdown').on('shown.bs.dropdown', function () {
                 var slider = $(this).find('.flexslider').data('flexslider');
                 $(window).trigger('resize');
                 slider.resize();
             });
 
             $("#navbar-menu .dropdown-menu").click(function (e) { e.stopPropagation(); });
 
             $("#btnSearch").click(function () {
 
                 var keyword = $("#txbKeyword").val();
 
                 if (keyword == "") {
                     alert("請輸入關鍵字");
                     return;
                 }
 
                 location.href = '/sites/ch/search.aspx?q=' + keyword;
 
             });
 
             $("#txbKeyword").keydown(function () {
 
                 var btnSearch = $("#btnSearch")
 
                 if (event.keyCode == 13) {
                     btnSearch.focus();
                 }
             });
         })
    </script>
